{"word":"καταπήγνυμι","slug":"καταπήγνυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταπήγνυμι</b></el> <el>(and <el>-ύω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πήξω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to stick fast in the ground, plant firmly</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> and plup. <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, <i>to stand fast</i> or <i>firm in</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>στήλη καταπεπηγυῖα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}